-dopamine-signals-for-learning-and-moving</link><description>张等人。测量执行决策任务的大鼠纹状体中多巴胺和乙酰胆碱的释放，发现胆碱能和多巴胺释放的相对时间控制多巴胺是否促进强化学习或运动活力。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/acetylcholine-demixes-heterogeneous-dopamine-signals-for-learning-and-moving.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 12:08:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/acetylcholine-demixes-heterogeneous-dopamine-signals-for-learning-and-moving</guid></item><item><title>PHF8在神经发生过程中对丝氨酸生物合成的表观遗传调控</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/epigenetic-regulation-of-serine-biosynthesis-by-phf8-during-neurogenesis</link><description>将表观遗传学和神经发生中的代谢联系起来！ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/epigenetic-regulation-of-serine-biosynthesis-by-phf8-during-neurogenesis2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 11:53:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/epigenetic-regulation-of-serine-biosynthesis-by-phf8-during-neurogenesis</guid></item><item><title>鼻拭子测试发现早期阿尔茨海默病信号</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nasal-swab-test-spots-early-alzheimers-signals</link><description>雪旺细胞来源的外泌体是神经修复的强大促进剂，能够在多种模型中增强轴突再生、髓鞘再生和功能恢复。这些效应是通过调节神经元、神经胶质细胞、内皮细胞和免疫细胞的多因子货物（miRNA、mRNA、蛋白质）介导的。重要的是，最初作为一种新颖的生物学见解现在正在迅速转向治疗创新。因此，雪旺细胞衍生的外泌体既代表了胶质细胞-神经元通讯的一种新模式，又代表了下一代神经再生疗法的有希望的途径。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nasal-swab-test-spots-early-alzheimers-signals2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 11:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nasal-swab-test-spots-early-alzheimers-signals</guid></item><item><title>JSPS 转型领域 (A) 2023–2028</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/jsps-transformative-area-a-2023-2028</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 11:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/jsps-transformative-area-a-2023-2028</guid></item><item><title>脂质运载蛋白 2 通过 AXL 协调抵抗铁死亡</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/lipocalin-2-orchestrates-resistance-to-ferroptosis-via-axl</link><description>王等人。显示 lipocalin-2 抑制胶质母细胞瘤中铁依赖性细胞死亡。靶向该通路中的多个成员可激活铁依赖性细胞死亡，增加小鼠模型的存活率，并证明了胶质母细胞瘤的潜在治疗方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/lipocalin-2-orchestrates-resistance-to-ferroptosis-via-axl2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 11:08:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/lipocalin-2-orchestrates-resistance-to-ferroptosis-via-axl</guid></item><item><title>一种全新的芳环烷基化方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-radical-new-way-to-alkylate-aromatic-rings</link><description>当化学家的控制反应产生意想不到的产物时，他们发现了光催化&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-radical-new-way-to-alkylate-aromatic-rings.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 10:53:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-radical-new-way-to-alkylate-aromatic-rings</guid></item><item><title>科学家以 3D 方式追踪蜜蜂并发现非凡的秘密导航技能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-track-bees-in-3d-and-discover-remarkable-secret-navigation-skills</link><description>蜜蜂以惊人的精确度沿着一致的、有地标引导的路线飞行，比它们的摇摆舞显示出更好的导航能力。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-track-bees-in-3d-and-discover-remarkable-secret-navigation-skills.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 10:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-track-bees-in-3d-and-discover-remarkable-secret-navigation-skills</guid></item></channel></rss>